overview: "The true essence of "Sex Clinic" is in the first scene with Baby Kitten and Mike Chapman. The way they play their characters is very entertaining, real fun and comedy. The movie has a lot of great scenes and performers, just to mention: Malena, Zaawadi, and Vince in one sceneare fantastic together. My favorite one is Charlie Forde with Raul Costa. Charlie is completely in character with Raul. Another remarkable scene is with Valentina and Vince, it's so hot. All the scenes in the movie are completely different." - Rocco Siffredi
title: Rocco's Sex Clinic: Treatment 4
